item.title: How do you add objects to your server?
item.dc:creator: @Solumstone Solumstone
item.description:
@Solumstone wrote:

Open your client. Ctrl+F and search for AddGlobalObj. There should be a big list of objects. Add them there. If there’s not, you need to get a source that has object adding readily available (because I don’t know how to change it so you can add them). Try Funscap3 PK. Just google it.
